---
title: Envelope Encryption Flow (SSE-KMS)
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant S3 as Amazon S3
    participant KMS as AWS KMS

    Note over App,KMS: UPLOAD (PutObject with SSE-KMS)
    App->>S3: PutObject (100MB file)
    S3->>KMS: GenerateDataKey(KeyId=cmk-123)
    KMS-->>S3: Plaintext data key + Encrypted data key
    Note over S3: Encrypt file with plaintext data key
    Note over S3: Discard plaintext key from memory
    Note over S3: Store: encrypted file + encrypted data key

    Note over App,KMS: DOWNLOAD (GetObject)
    App->>S3: GetObject
    S3->>KMS: Decrypt(encrypted data key)
    KMS-->>S3: Plaintext data key
    Note over S3: Decrypt file with plaintext data key
    S3-->>App: Plaintext file
    Note over S3: Discard plaintext key from memory
